:"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, saying, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWe endured those menses and we were ordered to make up missed fasts, but we were not ordered to make up missed prayers.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/ramadan-make-up-missed-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":27596,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Making up missed fasts throughout the year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cI had to make up some fasts I missed during the month of Ramadan, but I was unable to do so until the month of Sha\u2019ban as\u00a0I was busy with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/03\/women-hajj-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":27596,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women performing Hajj will menstruating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, enter my dwelling at Sarif while I was crying. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter? Are you menstruating?\u201d I said yes. The Prophet said, \u201cThis is a matter that Allah has decreed for the daughters of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13709,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/menses-not-in-your-hand\/","url_meta":{"origin":27596,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Menstruation: Your menses are not in your hand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to me, \u201cBring me a mat from the mosque.\u201d I said, \u201cI am menstruating.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYour menses are not in your hand.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 298 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27941,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/20\/fasts-mondays-thursdays\/","url_meta":{"origin":27596,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: The Prophet fasts on Mondays and Thursdays","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was eager to fast on Monday and Thursday. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 745 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u062a\u064e\u062d\u064e\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0635\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0650\u0627\u062b\u0652\u0646\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0633\u0650 745 \u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0631\u0645\u0630\u064a \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0648\u0645 \u0628\u0627\u0628 \u0645\u0627 \u062c\u0627\u0621 \u0641\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":118,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/21\/good-character-fasting-praying\/","url_meta":{"origin":27596,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Manners: Good character equals many fasts and prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 21, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer may reach by\u00a0his good character the rank\u00a0of one who regularly fasts and stands for prayer\u00a0at night.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4798 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u00a0\u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u